subject: RE: [junit] how do i start using Junit
msgSnippet: No need for that. You have to have the manual first before you can read it. Also the Junit manual is so buggy he s better off asking for help. Andoni. ...
messageBody:
No need for that. You have to have the manual first before you can read it.

Also the Junit manual is so buggy he's better off asking for help.

Andoni.
